This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses the use of GANs for generative adversarial attacks on machine learning models. It could also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as it deals with the security of machine learning models. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it mentions the use of GANs for generating images. It could also be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of deep learning techniques.
